<subSubSection pageId="8" pageNumber="9" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1436,151,320]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,151,176]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Remarks.</emphasis>
The species has been recorded from two localities in 
<collectingCountry box="[937,1041,151,176]" name="Denmark" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Denmark</collectingCountry>
(see data above), two localities in southern 
<collectingCountry box="[260,350,188,212]" name="Norway" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Norway</collectingCountry>
(
<emphasis box="[372,416,188,211]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">VAY</emphasis>
: Lista and 
<emphasis box="[558,588,189,212]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">RY</emphasis>
: Jaeren) (
<bibRefCitation author="Odegaard, F. &amp; Sverdrup-Thygeson, A. &amp; Hansen, L. O. &amp; Hanssen, O. &amp; Oberg, S." box="[703,960,188,213]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" refId="ref60082" refString="Odegaard, F., Sverdrup-Thygeson, A., Hansen, L. O., Hanssen, O. &amp; Oberg, S. (2009) Kartlegging av invertebrater i fem hotspot-habitattyper. Nye norske arter og rOdlistearter 2004 - 2008. NINA Rapport 500, 102 pp." type="book" year="2009">
Ødegaard 
<emphasis box="[826,888,188,213]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">et al.</emphasis>
2009
</bibRefCitation>
), and one locality in southwest 
<collectingCountry box="[1347,1436,188,213]" name="Sweden" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Sweden</collectingCountry>
(
<collectingRegion box="[158,250,223,248]" country="Sweden" name="Halland" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Halland</collectingRegion>
) (
<bibRefCitation author="Fritz, O. &amp; Larsson, K." box="[277,538,223,248]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" refId="ref54885" refString="Fritz, O. &amp; Larsson, K. (2010) Hoga naturvarden i grus- och sandtakter i Hallands lan. Lansstyrelsen i Hallands lan, rapport nr 2010: 17, 168 pp." type="book" year="2010">Fritz &amp; Larsson 2010</bibRefCitation>
). The closest records outside the Nordic countries are from northern 
<collectingCountry box="[1358,1436,223,248]" name="Poland" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Poland</collectingCountry>
(
<collectingRegion box="[158,282,260,285]" country="Poland" name="Zachodniopomorskie" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Pomerania</collectingRegion>
) (
<bibRefCitation author="Noskiewicz, J. &amp; Pulawski, W." box="[305,648,260,285]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" pagination="1 - 65" refId="ref59821" refString="Noskiewicz, J. &amp; Pulawski, W. (1958) Klucze do oznaczania owadow Polski [Keys for the Identification of Polish Insects], Czesc XXIV Blonkowki - Hymenoptera, Zeszyt 55 - 56 Zlotolitki - Chrysididae, Cleptidae. Polski Zwiazek Entomologiczny, 23, 1 - 65." type="journal article" year="1958">Noskiewicz &amp; Puławski 1958</bibRefCitation>
). In 
<collectingCountry box="[700,791,260,284]" name="Norway" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Norway</collectingCountry>
, the species has been classified as vulnerable (
<bibRefCitation author="Hansen, L. O. &amp; Lonnve, O. J. &amp; Odegaard, F." pageId="8" pageNumber="9" pagination="331 - 346" refId="ref55334" refString="Hansen, L. O., Lonnve, O. J. &amp; Odegaard, F. (2010) Veps, Hymenoptera. In: Kalas, J. A., Viken, A., Henriksen, S. &amp; Skjelseth, S. (Eds.), The 2010 Norwegian Red List for Species. The Norwegian Biodiversity Information Centre, Norway, pp. 331 - 346." type="book chapter" year="2010">
Hansen 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">et al.</emphasis>
2010
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
